message: "Human trafficking is a crime that exploits another person's liberty, and can result in lasting trauma to victims."

data.description: MILWAUKEE -- Under-reported and oftentimes undetected, human trafficking impacts millions of people around the world, including in southeast Wisconsin. data.title: ‘Hidden issue:’ Rotary Club talks human trafficking in Milwaukee, what’s being done to fight it
